Package
Description
com.ubicua.didas.authentication
Extends WebAuthnAuthenticator class and validates whether a user is authorized to grant access permissions for a vehicle to view this user's account data during the authorization process.
com.ubicua.didas.resources
Extends JpaRealmProvider class creating default attributes for specific client roles that will be used to configure the DID document generated by the Didas DidasClientDiscoveryProvider well-known discovery service.
com.ubicua.didas.rest
REST resource providers for managing client roles, user profiles, custom components and exposing the Didas DidasClientDiscoveryProvider well-known discovery service.
com.ubicua.didas.ui
Custom admin UI page and tab used by the Didas DidasClientDiscoveryProvider well-known discovery service.
com.ubicua.didas.userprofile
Extends UserProfileProvider class with additional request-time logic: creates or updates Didas-specific custom vehicle attributes for declarative user profile.
